    LCARS (Library Computer Access/Retrieval System) Theme
    Inspired by Star Trek: The Next Generation's futuristic interface design
    
    Classic LCARS Color Palette from thelcars.com:
    - African Violet #CC99FF - Tertiary elements
    - Almond #FFAA00 - Buttons, interactive
    - Blue #5588FF - Info, status
    - Butterscotch #FF9966 - Warm accents
    - Gold #FFCC00 - Primary interactive
    - Golden Orange #FF9900 - Alerts
    - Gray #666688 - Inactive
    - Green #99CC33 - Success
    - Ice #99CCFF - Cool accents
    - Lilac #CC55FF - Special elements
    - Magenta #CC5599 - Tertiary
    - Mars #990011 - Critical alerts
    - Orange #FF8800 - Secondary actions
    - Peach #FF8855 - Warm highlights
    - Red #CC4444 - Warnings
    - Sky #AAAAFF - Backgrounds
    - Sunflower #FFCC99 - Highlights
    - Tomato #FF5555 - Alerts
    - Violet Creme #DDBBFF - Soft accents
